description:
Beautifully presented and with stunning views of the parkland, this spacious and beautifully presented townhouse is the ultimate in relaxed lifestyle living. Whether you are a keen golfer or you are just searching for a home with serenity, this property is a must to view.

Whether you are entertaining friends in the courtyard enjoying the tranquillity and privacy or taking in the views and reading a book on the upper balcony, the choice is yours to enjoy.

Offering a perfect combination of natural light and stunning décor, this townhouse has a fantastic floor plan, spacious and inviting. With a beautifully designed kitchen featuring spacious benchtops, quality appliances and walk in pantry, all you need to do is move in and enjoy it.

Additional features:

• 3 Bedrooms with built ins and ceiling fans

• Main bedroom with ensuite

• Open plan kitchen, dishwasher, walk in pantry

• Fully screened

• Expansive courtyard with rear access gate to parkland

• Covered balcony upstairs leading from the main bedroom

• Fully fenced

• End townhouse

You have peace of mind with 24 hours security and access to pool, tennis courts and community centre. It is also within walking distance to the local shops, bus stop and local schools.




Disclaimer: The above information is accurate to the best of our knowledge; however, we advise that all interested parties make their own enquiries as we will not be held responsible for any variation that may apply to this information.
